summary: an animated short about the fluidity of identity – whether it’s sexuality, gender identity, or personality – and the role of...
caption:
an animated short about the fluidity of identity – whether it’s sexuality, gender identity, or personality – and the role of labels in our lives. It is based on @danielhowell’s response to a question posed during his March 2017 liveshow: “I’m ace, but what if I change my mind?”

yes, this is what has kept me busy the entire week! this one goes to @brown-eyeddd for the continued support since my first art upload, with special thanks to @moonchair for bringing my attention to dan’s thoughts on the matter with their gif of this moment a year ago.
